## Project Overview
**DotERP** is the **QuickBooks for DAOs** — a full ERP suite for treasury, payroll, invoicing, HR, and analytics — **built natively on Polkadot**.

**Problem**: DAOs manage $1B+ using Google Sheets and Discord.  
**Solution**: All-in-one, on-chain, open-source ERP with Substrate pallets and ink! contracts.

**Impact**: 10,000+ DAOs on Polkadot run operations transparently, automatically, and securely.

## Milestones
| Milestone | Deliverable | Timeline | Budget |
|-----------|-------------|----------|--------|
| M1: Core Treasury | Multisig + voting pallet + React dashboard (testnet) | 6 weeks | $15k |
| M2: Payroll & Invoices | ink! batch payouts + XCM-ready invoices | 8 weeks | $20k |
| M3: HR & Analytics | Identity integration + SubQuery dashboards | 6 weeks | $15k |
| M4: Launch | Mobile app, docs, mainnet deploy | 4 weeks | $10k |

**Success Metrics**: 100+ GitHub stars, 10 DAO pilots, $1M+ in on-chain volume.

## Tech Stack
- **Backend**: Substrate Node + custom pallets (Rust)
- **Contracts**: ink! (Rust)
- **Frontend**: React + Polkadot.js
- **Data**: SubQuery + IPFS
- **License**: MIT

- **Why Web3F**: Accelerates Polkadot as the enterprise blockchain for DAOs.
